This is a heartfelt tribute to the one and only living legend, Damith Asanka. For the first time ever, a rising young band - Yaka Crew - takes on these legendary songs with respect, energy, and soul.
We grew up listening to his voice. Now we honor it with ours.
Hope you feel the love in every note. 

A massive thank you to every single soul who stood behind this project.
I won’t list names here, not out of disrespect, but to preserve the clean focus of this tribute.
But know this: you are the reason this happened.
To the Lighting crew, LED team, Sound crew, Engineers, Video team, Backing Vocal Crew and my beloved friends! you are the best.Your effort, your energy, your belief… I’ll carry it with me always. ❤️
-Chanuka Mora-
